                           HistoryMetacardImpl.Action action,
                           org.apache.shiro.subject.Subject subject)
        Will convert the given Metacard to a HistoryMetacardImpl by cloning it and adding the current subject, time, and a random UUID. Cannot take a HistoryMetacardImpl as the sourceMetacard.
        Parameters:
        sourceMetacard - Metacard to clone and create a history item from
        action - Which action was done to modify the metacard
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException
